    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives super smoothly and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and performs even better, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
