    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound FD3S RX-7 featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across both rotors, with a seamless transition between the primary and secondary turbochargers. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a four-wheel double-wishbone suspension setup that has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings to minimize deflection. To ensure thermal efficiency, an upgraded dual-pass aluminum radiator has been installed to mitigate heat soak during spirited driving. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina, the structural integrity and mechanical performance remain sharp. This is a purist\u2019s setup, dialed in for throttle response and lateral grip.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Interior is clean.",
