      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it! It's been a wonderful, reliable companion and is still in really solid shape. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, it drives like a dream and has been well-loved. I've taken great care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014it's a fantastic ride at a great price!",
      "price": 31500.0,
