      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering precise engagement and tactile feedback. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate floor fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced. The suspension maintains factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the signature M-chassis balance. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight, and the M-variable differential lock operates flawlessly under load. A true driver\u2019s spec for those who value mechanical integrity over concours paint.",
